developer: DELIIV - SERVICOS E COMERCIO, SOCIEDADE UNIPESSOAL LDA
description:
Receba comida entregue diretamente à sua porta a partir de uma ampla seleção de restaurantes locais em Praia. Quer esteja com vontade de saborear o seu prato preferido ou experimentar algo novo, o Deliiv facilita o pedido dos melhores locais da cidade. Acompanhe o seu pedido em tempo real para uma experiência de entrega tranquila.

ENCONTRE SEU RESTAURANTE FAVORITO
Peça de restaurantes próximos e explore opções por tipo de cozinha, nome do restaurante ou pratos específicos. Com o Deliiv, você pode desfrutar de uma variedade de escolhas, como pizza, hambúrgueres, sushi, comida chinesa e muito mais.
Prefere retirar seu pedido? Pule as filas e escolha a opção de retirada com facilidade. As suas refeições favoritas e opções de entrega estão a apenas um toque de distância com o Deliiv.

PEÇA UMA VARIEDADE DE PRODUTOS ESSENCIAIS
Precisa de mais do que apenas comida? Peça itens domésticos de supermercados locais, drogarias e lojas de animais. Encontre de tudo, desde produtos para bebês e itens de farmácia até alimentos frescos como frutas e pão, além de produtos congelados. Também pode encomendar flores, cosméticos e produtos de beleza.

PROCESSO DE PEDIDO SIMPLES
Explore os menus, escolha seus pratos favoritos e adicione-os ao carrinho em apenas alguns toques. O Deliiv torna o pedido de comida para entrega ou retirada rápido e fácil. Também pode agendar o seu pedido com antecedência e recebê-lo na hora que precisar.

ACOMPANHAMENTO EM TEMPO REAL
Acompanhe sua entrega em um mapa ao vivo à medida que se dirige ao seu endereço. Fique informado com o tempo estimado de entrega e receba notificações assim que o pedido chegar à sua porta.

SOBRE O DELIIV
O Deliiv é a sua plataforma ideal para entrega de comida em Praia. Oferecendo uma maneira fácil e confiável de desfrutar de refeições dos seus restaurantes locais favoritos, o Deliiv proporciona uma experiência de alta qualidade do início ao fim.

DISPONÍVEL EM PRAIA
O Deliiv está atualmente disponível em Praia, com planos para expandir para mais cidades de Cabo Verde em breve. Fique atento para novidades!

TheFork is Europe’s leading restaurant booking platform, proudly bringing people together through unique and affordable culinary experiences since 2007. What are you waiting for? Activate your location and we’ll activate your taste buds! You set the tone, we set the table.

1 reservation = 100 Yums (Y)

EggRow Keeper is a charming fridge inventory app with a unique twist — everything is designed around the metaphor of eggs in a refrigerator. The interface looks like a cozy fridge, and each product is visualized as an item in a nest, with eggs taking center stage. It helps users track food items, monitor expiration dates, estimate the total value of their fridge, and manage a shopping list — all wrapped in a light-hearted, visually engaging experience.

The main screen displays your virtual fridge with organized shelves. You can add products manually, specifying name, category, quantity, purchase date, and expiration. Categories include dairy, vegetables, meat, eggs, and others — each placed on its own "shelf." Eggs are treated as a special product type, displayed in a dedicated egg tray. When an item expires, it’s marked with a distinct “rotten egg” icon for quick recognition. You can also view a filtered list of soon-to-expire or missing items.

EggRow Keeper includes a simple analysis tool. When adding items, you can enter their price (per unit, kilogram, liter, etc.). The app then calculates the total "value" of your fridge contents. A category breakdown shows where most of your spending goes (e.g., "Dairy — 38%"). It also keeps track of patterns — how often you buy eggs, which items run out the fastest, and more.

The integrated shopping list helps with restocking. Items that are out of stock are suggested for the list automatically, but you can add or remove anything manually. Once an item is marked “purchased,” it can be moved directly into your fridge. You can also sort the list by category, making trips to the store more efficient.

A unique feature of the app is the “Egg of the Day” — a daily card offering a fun fact, quote, or practical food storage tip. The cards come in various humorous moods like “The Philosopher Egg” or “The Proud Egg.” You can save these cards to your gallery or share them with friends on social media.

Additional settings include expiration reminders, currency and unit preferences, data reset, and access to the privacy policy and developer info. EggRow Keeper offers a practical yet playful approach to home food organization — especially for egg lovers.

Tired of cooking the same 3 meals on repeat? Zest integrates a mind-blowing cooking education into your routine. Learn to cook with us through step-by-step explanations of foundational cooking concepts in fewer than 10 minutes and dishes that bring the concept to life. Our recipes are created by two former Michelin star chefs, distilled by a home chef, and cooked by you, the superstar home cook that you are (or will be). We don't assume any prior culinary knowledge. We meet you where you are and help you improve.
 
Stop copying traditional recipes - start learning from Zest. We've cooked those delicious Bon Appetit dinners. But when we took away the recipes we felt like lost puppies. Zest is designed to teach you the how's and why's of cooking. So when the recipe is gone you can confidently navigate the kitchen. The promise: Taste improvement after one dinner with Zest.

FEATURES:

STEP-BY-STEP INSTRUCTIONS
We've all tried cooking a TikTok recipe. You rewatch the video 13 times to figure out what the hell is going on. Zest embeds videos throughout recipes so you can click into content when you need it. No more pausing and restarting. Learn at your own pace.
 
CONCEPT VIDEOS
Watch a short video on a new concept at your own pace and then cook recipes that reinforce what you've learned. We dive into topics like the science of tasting and the basics of seasoning, sautéing, roasting and more!

SKILL VIDEOS
Don't know how to dice an onion? Don't be embarrassed, we got you covered. Skill videos are linked in each recipe to guide you along, so you don't have to watch Gordon Ramsey on YouTube (we love his accent too).

CURATED MENU
Choose a menu to fit your preferences. Tired of wasting produce? Search for dishes including what’s already in your fridge. Got allergies? Compile safe recipes in your menu to find them when you’re ready to get cooking. 

GROCERY LIST
Shop your menu with our automated grocery list. Plus, utilize our helpful tips while you shop. Don't know what a neutral oil is? We got you covered.
